<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Application Update</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #3d016f;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 20px;
            background: #fff;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        .next-steps {
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .social-links {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .social-links a {
            color: #3d016f;
            margin: 0 10px;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 20px;
            padding: 20px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #666;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>Application Update</h1>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
        <p>Dear <%= applicantName %>,</p>

        <p>Thank you for your interest in our Tech Internship Bootcamp and for taking the time to apply for the <%= track %> program.</p>

        <p>After careful consideration of your application, we regret to inform you that we are unable to offer you a place in this cohort. While your application showed merit, we received an overwhelming number of qualified candidates and had limited spots available.</p>

        <div class="next-steps">
            <h3>We encourage you to:</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>Apply for our next cohort starting <%= nextCohortDate %></li>
                <li>Continue developing your portfolio</li>
                <li>Follow us on social media for future opportunities</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <p>We wish you the best in your professional journey.</p>

        <p>Regards,<br>
        Rhedge Studios Tech Bootcamp Team</p>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
        <p>Â© <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Rhedge Studios. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
